    <thetext>Description of problem:

After upgrading to f24 (so upgrading from hexchat 2.10.2-4.f23 to hexchat 2.12.1-2.f24), the input box and topic box does not respect the &quot;Use the Text box font and colors&quot; settings.

Even with this setting, they are still white.


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):

hexchat-2.12.1-2.fc24.x86_64


How reproducible:

Always.


Steps to Reproduce:
1. upgrade to f24 or clean install
2. install hexchat
3. change the settings to &quot;Use the Text box font and colors&quot;


Actual results:

The input and topic box are still white.


Expected results:

They change to match the hexchat theme.


Additional info:</thetext>
